flace - Find and repLACE editing tools for python
=================================================

VERSION {version}

With ``flace`` you can search and edit files in various ways. 

Examples
--------

Search for matching strings in a file::

   import flace
   
   flace.mgrep("file_path", ["search_string_1", "search_string_2", ...])


   
